### MOLE Backend API — REST Client
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension (or use as reference)
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# HEALTH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AUTH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register (Generator)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.generator@mole.np",
  "password": "password123",
  "full_name": "Test Generator",
  "role": "generator",
  "location": "Bhaktapur"
}

###

### Register (Buyer)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.buyer@mole.np",
  "password": "password123",
  "full_name": "Test Buyer",
  "role": "buyer",
  "industry": "Biomass energy plants",
  "location": "Patan"
}

###

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.generator@mole.np",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Get Current User
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# LISTINGS
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get All Listings (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/listings

###

### Get Listings — filtered by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/listings?category=wood_biomass&page=1&limit=10

###

### Get Listings — filtered by neighborhood
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/listings?neighborhood=Bhaktapur

###

### Get Single Listing
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/listings/LISTING_ID_HERE

###

### Create Listing (auth required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/listings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Hardwood Offcuts — काठको धुलो",
  "category_code": "wood_biomass",
  "material_type": "Hardwood offcuts and sawdust",
  "quantity_kg": 300,
  "condition": "Clean",
  "price_npr_min": 4,
  "price_npr_max": 7,
  "neighborhood": "Bhaktapur / Thimi",
  "lat": 27.6727,
  "lng": 85.3990
}

###

### Update Listing Status (owner only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/listings/LISTING_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "sold"
}

###

### Delete Listing (owner only)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/listings/LISTING_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MATCHES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Matched Listings for Buyer (auth required)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/matches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Express Interest in a Listing
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/matches
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "listing_id": "LISTING_ID_HERE"
}

###

### Update Match Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/matches/MATCH_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "contacted"
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AI CLASSIFY
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Available Fallback Responses (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/fallbacks

###

### Classify Waste Image (auth required)
### Note: Use multipart/form-data with field name "image"
### In REST Client: use a real image file path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/ai/classify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="waste.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
------FormBoundary--

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# IMPACT
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get Platform Impact Stats (public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/impact

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# CATEGORIES
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get All Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories

###

### Get Single Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/wood_biomass
